#! <COMMENTS>
#! <COMMENT
#!   IDENTIFIER="303"
#!   COMMENT_VALUE="&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;&#10;p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }&#10;&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;MS Shell Dlg 2&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;This section utilizes mulitple instances of the METADATA_VALUE_MAPPER to correct values to valid English values and to add the valid French equivalents and RI_CODES where applicable.  It can be utilized for mulitple metadata items by accessing custom look up tables applicable to specific items.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;Turn the  error mapping options and the data items to be mapped on or off by clicking on the transformer and selecting yes/no.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - ERROR_NOT_MAPPED: enables mapping of data item values that cannot be found in the lookup tables.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - ENGLISH_REFRESH: enables updating of English attribute values.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - FRENCH_REFRESH: enables updating of French attribute values.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - CODE_REFRESH: enables updating of RI_CODE values.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;Enter the attribute key name by clicking on the transformer and selecting the drop down menu next to the &apos;att_to_map&apos; text box and selecting the &apos;Open text editor...&apos; option.  Explicitly enter the attribute key name in the text editor (ie: contacts{}.role).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt; Do not select the &apos;Attribute Value&apos; option from the drop down menu to select the attribute key name.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;"
#!   POSITION="10196.100057279402 -306.70304913206439"
#!   TOP_LEFT="10196.100057279402 -306.70304913206439"
#!   BOTTOM_RIGHT="12554.423921768046 -674.20642416581472"
#!   BOUNDING_RECT="10196.100057279402 -306.70304913206439 2358.3238644886446 367.50337503375033"
