#!   COLOUR="0.058823529411764705,0.72156862745098038,0.31372549019607843,0.39215686274509803"
#!   SIZE_POLICY="10"
#!   ANCHORED_NODE="0"
#! />
#! <COMMENT
#!   IDENTIFIER="304"
#!   COMMENT_VALUE="&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;&#10;p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }&#10;&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;MS Shell Dlg 2&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;This section utilizes the METADATA_FORMAT_MAPPER to correct data format values to valid data format values and to associate and add the French and English &apos;Resource Type&apos; attribute to each data format type. It accesses a custom look up table applicable to data formats.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;Turn the error mapping options and the data items to be mapped on or off by clicking on the transformer and selecting yes/no.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - ERROR_NOT_MAPPED: enables mapping of data item values that cannot be found in the lookup tables.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - REAL_VALUE_REFRESH: enables updating of data format attribute values.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - RES_TYPE_FR_REFRESH: enables mapping of French resource types.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;  - RES_TYPE_EN_REFRESH: enables mapping of English resource types.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;Enter the attribute key name by clicking on the transformer and selecting the drop down menu next to the &apos;att_to_map&apos; text box and selecting the &apos;Open text editor...&apos; option.  Explicitly enter the attribute key name in the text editor (ie: resources{}.format).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;Do not select the &apos;Attribute Value&apos; option from the drop down menu to select the attribute key name.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;"
